---

<Layout title="César Adrián Morado | Portfolio Premium" description="Frontend Developer Senior | Construyo experiencias digitales modernas, rápidas y escalables con Astro, Angular y React.">
  <main class="w-full relative">
    
    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section id="home" class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center pt-24 pb-16 overflow-hidden px-4">
      <!-- 3D Particle Canvas Background -->
      <canvas id="hero-particles" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full pointer-events-auto z-0"></canvas>
      
      <!-- Gradient Mesh Overlay -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_80%_20%,rgba(109,94,249,0.12),transparent_50%),radial-gradient(circle_at_20%_80%,rgba(0,212,255,0.12),transparent_50%)] pointer-events-none z-0"></div>
      
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center relative z-10">
        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 flex flex-col items-start text-left space-y-6">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-accent animate-pulse">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span> Disponible para nuevos proyectos
          </div>
          
          <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-display font-bold tracking-tight leading-none text-white">
            Hola, soy <br/>
            <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary via-secondary to-accent bg-clip-text text-transparent drop-shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(109,94,249,0.3)]">César Adrián Morado</span>
          </h1>
          
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-3xl font-display font-medium text-accent">
            Frontend Developer Senior
          </h2>
          
          <p class="text-text-muted text-base sm:text-lg max-w-xl">
            Construyo experiencias digitales modernas, rápidas y escalables. Apasionado por la interactividad, el rendimiento excepcional y los detalles que marcan la diferencia.
          </p>
          
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 pt-2">
            <a href="#projects" class="px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary hover:shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(109,94,249,0.5)] text-white font-bold text-sm tracking-wide transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 border border-primary/20 hover:border-accent">
              Ver proyectos
            </a>
            <a href="#contact" class="px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full bg-card-dark/60 hover:bg-card-dark/80 text-white font-bold text-sm tracking-wide border border-white/10 hover:border-accent/40 transition-all duration-300 backdrop-blur-sm transform hover:-translate-y-0.5">
              Contactar
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 3D Futuristic Wireframe Render (CSS/HTML) -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 hidden lg:flex justify-center items-center relative h-[450px]">
          <!-- Glowing mesh container -->
          <div class="relative w-[320px] h-[320px] flex items-center justify-center">
            <!-- Glow background -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/20 rounded-full blur-[80px] animate-pulse"></div>
            <!-- Outer Ring -->
            <div class="absolute w-full h-full rounded-full border border-dashed border-accent/30 animate-[spin_40s_linear_infinite]"></div>
            <!-- Middle Ring -->
            <div class="absolute w-[80%] h-[80%] rounded-full border border-primary/40 animate-[spin_20s_linear_infinite_reverse]"></div>
            <!-- Inner Orb -->
            <div class="absolute w-[60%] h-[60%] rounded-full bg-gradient-to-tr from-primary to-accent opacity-20 blur-[10px] animate-pulse"></div>
            <!-- Futuristic Floating Cubes (CSS Art) -->
            <div class="absolute w-24 h-24 bg-card-dark/70 border-2 border-accent rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center transform -rotate-12 hover:rotate-12 transition-transform duration-500 shadow-2xl backdrop-blur-md">
              <span class="text-4xl text-accent font-display font-bold">&lt;/&gt;</span>
            </div>
            <!-- Floating particles and icons around -->
            <div class="absolute -top-4 right-10 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#dd0031]/10 border border-[#dd0031]/30 flex items-center justify-center text-[#dd0031] text-[10px] font-bold shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(221,0,49,0.3)] animate-bounce">Ng</div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-4 -left-2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#61dafb]/10 border border-[#61dafb]/30 flex items-center justify-center text-[#61dafb] text-xs font-bold shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(97,218,251,0.3)] animate-bounce [animation-delay:1s]">Re</div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-16 right-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#ff5d00]/10 border border-[#ff5d00]/30 flex items-center justify-center text-[#ff5d00] text-xs font-bold shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(255,93,0,0.3)] animate-bounce [animation-delay:1.5s]">As</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SOBRE MÍ SECTION -->
    <section id="about" class="py-24 px-4 max-w-7xl mx-auto relative space-y-24">
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-80 h-80 bg-secondary/5 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 left-0 w-80 h-80 bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>

      <!-- 1. Hero / Main Info Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-center">
        <!-- Columna izquierda: Tarjeta Premium -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 relative group" id="about-card-anim">
          <div class="absolute -inset-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent rounded-3xl opacity-30 blur-lg group-hover:opacity-60 transition duration-1000 group-hover:duration-200"></div>
          <div class="relative rounded-3xl border border-white/10 overflow-hidden bg-card-dark shadow-2xl p-6 space-y-6 tilt-card">
            <!-- Marco glow con foto -->
            <div class="relative aspect-square w-full rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10 group-hover:border-accent/50 transition-colors duration-500 shadow-inner">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-bg-dark/80 via-transparent to-transparent z-10"></div>
              <img src="/1757554006561.jpg" alt="César Adrián Morado" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" />
            </div>

            <!-- Metadata List -->
            <div class="space-y-3 font-sans text-sm text-text-muted">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="text-accent text-base select-none">💻</span>
                <span class="font-semibold text-white">Frontend Developer</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="text-accent text-base select-none">📍</span>
                <span>Celaya, Guanajuato, México</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="text-accent text-base select-none">🏛️</span>
                <span>Instituto Electoral de Guanajuato</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="text-accent text-base select-none">🎓</span>
                <span>Ingeniero en Tecnologías de la Información</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="text-accent text-base select-none">🎓</span>
                <span>Maestría en Desarrollo de Interfaces Web (UNIR)</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Download CV Button -->
            <a 
              href="/Ing-Cesar-Adrian-Morado-Rodriguez-2026.pdf" 
              download 
              class="block w-full py-3.5 text-center text-xs font-bold text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(109,94,249,0.4)] rounded-xl border border-primary/20 hover:border-accent transition-all duration-300 uppercase tracking-wider cursor-pointer"
            >
              Descargar CV
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Columna derecha: Historia profesional -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-6">
          <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-white tracking-tight">
            Sobre <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary via-secondary to-accent bg-clip-text text-transparent">Mí</span>
          </h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-4 text-text-muted text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed font-sans">
            <p>
              Me especializo en diseñar y construir interfaces de usuario de alto impacto: rápidas, accesibles y con un rendimiento excepcional. Creo firmemente que el desarrollo frontend es el puente que conecta la complejidad de los datos con una experiencia de usuario intuitiva y fluida.
            </p>
            <p>
              A lo largo de mi trayectoria, he diseñado y desarrollado sistemas web en sectores de alta exigencia (salud, electoral y civil), enfocándome en crear arquitecturas sólidas, escalables y fáciles de mantener utilizando tecnologías modernas como Angular, TypeScript, Astro y C#.
            </p>
            <p>
              Mi enfoque no solo está en escribir código limpio, sino también en el impacto real del producto: optimizar tiempos de carga, asegurar la accesibilidad universal y alinear las mejores prácticas de UX con las necesidades operativas de los usuarios.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2. Filosofía, Actualmente & Hacia dónde voy (3-Card Grid) -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Filosofía -->
        <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 bg-card-dark/40 flex flex-col justify-between space-y-6">
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4 text-accent">
              <span class="text-xl select-none">💡</span>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-display font-bold text-white">Mi filosofía como desarrollador</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-xs sm:text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans italic">
              "Creo que una buena interfaz no solo debe verse bien; debe facilitar el trabajo de las personas, resolver problemas reales y ofrecer una experiencia intuitiva. Mi objetivo es construir aplicaciones mantenibles, rápidas y accesibles, cuidando tanto la experiencia del usuario como la calidad del código."
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent rounded-full"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Actualmente -->
        <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 bg-card-dark/40 space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-accent">
            <span class="text-xl select-none">📌</span>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-display font-bold text-white">Actualmente</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-3 font-sans text-xs sm:text-sm text-text-muted">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
